DESCRIPTION:Due to phenomenal demand\, smash-hit comedian\, best-selling au
 thor\, podcast host and viral online star Emma Doran has added a second sho
 w during this year's Galway Comedy Festival. There's no such thing as a per
 fect family\, but she wouldn't want one anyway... The many trials and tribu
 lations of Emma's blended family are laid bare\, womanhood examined\, and r
 elationships put to the test in this witty\, rambunctious show from one of 
